James B. BRYAN, District Director, v. YEE KAM CHONG. No. 7898. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. June 17, 1935. Ingram M. Stainback, U. S. Atty., of Honolulu, T. H., for appellant. Ebert J. Botts, of Honolulu, T. H., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, DENMAN, and MATHEWS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed, decree of dismissal filed and entered accordingly, and mandate of this court issued forthwith.
